Subject: drm/i915: Fix oops due to missing stack depot
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Alt-commit: 751a9d69b19702af35b0fedfb8ff362027c1cf0c
Git-commit: eb48d42198792f1330bbb3e82ac725d43c13fe02
